  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 28,000 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bbe \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "28,000 tourists visit Sri Lanka in July",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan Tourism Development Authority has reported that the number of foreign tourists who visited the country from 1st July to 19th this year is 28,733.",
        "Accordingly, the total number of foreign tourists arriving in the country so far in 2022 is 440,110.",
        "The data shows that tourist arrivals to the country are low but stable and indicate that tourists are interested in Sri Lanka despite the country's political and economic turmoil.",
        "A total of 4,714 people have arrived from England during the period from 1st July to 19th July.",
        "India is second with 3,375 arrivals. Germany is third with 2,322\u00a0tourists.",
        "Other notable markets for July include Canada, France, Switzerland and Australia.",
        "An overall analysis of total arrivals for the year ended July 19 shows that India tops the list as the largest contributor to Sri Lanka's tourism traffic. 72,136 tourists from India came from the country.",
        "England came second with 54,336 tourist arrivals. Russia ranks third with 47,412 tourist arrivals.",
        "However, as newly elected President Ranil Wickremesinghe has reimposed the state of emergency in the country, the number of arrivals is likely to decrease further."
      ],
